hadiths[107]{hadithnumber,text}:
3550,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik chadar odh kar namaz padhi jis mein naqsh aur nigaar they. phir farmaya : mujhey uskey naqsh aur nigaar ney mashghool kar diya. isey Abu-Jahm (Raziallahu anhu) key paas ley jao aur un sey un ki saada chadar ley aao."
3551,"Hazrat Abu-Barda (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa. unhoney mujhey eik mota teh band dikhaya jo Yamen mein banaya jata hai, aur eik chadar dikhai jisey malbada kehtey hain. unhoney qism kha kar farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) un do kapdon mein faut huye they."
3552,Hazrat Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik chadar odh kar namaz padhi jis par gireh laga rakhi thi.
3553,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath tha jabkey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney motey kinarey wali najraani chadar odh rakhi thi."
3554,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kabhi kisi ko gaali detey nahin dekha, aur na aap key liye kapda lapet kar rakha jata tha  (eik hi joda hota tha)."
3555,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik khatoon Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat main eik chadar ley kar hazir huin aur arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! mainey ye chadar apney haath sey buni hai taake aap ko pehnaaun. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wo chadar le li kyonkey aap ko uski zarurat thi . aap ghar sey tashrif laye to wo chadar tehband key tor par pehan rakhi thi. falan aadmi aaya. Hazrat Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ney us din us shakhs ka naam bhi liya tha (baad mein Raavi ko yad nahin raha.) us aadmi ney kaha aey Allah key Rasool! ye chadar kitni achi hai ! mujhey inayat farma dijiye. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : achcha . jab aap ghar tashrif ley gaey to wo chadar teh kar key us Sabab key yahan bhej di. logon ney usey kaha : Allah ki qasam! tu ney achcha nahin kya. ye chadar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh ki gaee thi . aur aap ko uski zarurat bhi thi wo tu ney aap sey mang li, halanke tujhey malum tha ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi ka sawal radd nahin kartey . usney kaha qism hai Allah ki! mainey aap sey ye chadar pehanney key liye nahin maangi balke isliye maangi hai ke wo mera kafan baney. Hazrat Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : jis din wo sahab faut huye, wo chadar (bhi) unka kafan thi."
3556,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney oon ka (saada aur mota) libas pahna hai, marammat shuda joota pahna hai aur intehai mota kapda zeb tan farmaya hai."
3557,"Hazrat abu-Umama sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney naya kapda pehna to farmaya : (الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ الَّذِي كَسَانِي مَا أُوَارِي بِهِ عَوْرَتِي وَأَتَجَمَّلُ بِهِ فِي حَيَاتِي) Allah ka shukr hai jisney mujhey wo kapda pehnaya jis sey mein apna satar chhipata hun aur zindagi mein us sey zeenat hasil karta hun : phir Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshad Mubarak suna hai : jisney naya kapda pahna aur kaha : (الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ الَّذِي كَسَانِي مَا أُوَارِي بِهِ عَوْرَتِي وَأَتَجَمَّلُ بِهِ فِي حَيَاتِي) phir jo purana kapda utara hai usey sadqa kar diya, wo zindagi mein aur wafat key baad Allah key muhabbat key saye mein, Allah ki hifazat mein aur Allah ki parda poshi mein rahega. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney teen baar ye baat irshad farmaai."
3558,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko safed qamis pehney dekha to farmaya : tumhara ye libas dhula huwa hai ya naya hai? unhoney kaha : nahin, balke dhula huwa hai. aap ney farmaya : ( الْبَسْ جَدِيدًا وَعِشْ حَمِيدًا وَمُتْ شَهِيدًا ) tumhein naya libas, qabile-tareef zindagi aur shahadat ki maut nasib ho."
3559,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney do tarah libas pehanney sey mana farmaya. libas pehanney key ye do (mamnua) andaz hain : chadar ko is andaz sey jism par lapetna ke haathon aur baazuon ko harkat dena mushkil ho jaey. aur eik kapdey mein is tarah bethna ke chhipaney waley hissey zahir honey ka andesha ho."
3560,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney do andaz sey libas pehanney sey mana farmaya : Ishtimaale-Samma sey aur eik kapdey key sath is tarah ehtiba karney sey key aasman ki taraf uska satar khula huwa ho.
3561,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney do andaz sey libas pehanney sey mana farmaya : Ishtimale-Samma sey aur eik kapdey ke sath is tarah ehtiba karney sey ke tumhaara satar aasman ki taraf khula ho."
3562,"Hazrat abu-Barda (Rahimahullah) apney walid (Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey huye farmatey hain ke unhoney mujh sey farmaya : beta! kaash! tum ney hamen us waqt dekha hota jab hum Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath hotey they, jab hum par barish ho jati to (aisi bu paida hoti ke) tum hamari bu ko bhedon ki bu samajhtey."
3563,"Hazrat Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik din Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (ghar sey) hamarey paas tashrif laye to aap ney oon ka buna huwa, tang aastinon wala eik rumi jubba pehan rakha tha. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney usi libas mein hamen namaz padhaai jabke aap key jism Mubarak par aur koi kapda na tha."
3564,"Hazrat Salman Faarsi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wuzu kya, phir jism Mubarak par pahna huwa ooni jubba ulta kar us sey chehra Mubarak poonchh liya."
3565,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap bakriyon key kanon par nishan laga rahey they. aur mainey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko eik chadar teh band key tor par baandhey huye dekha."
3566,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumharey behtareen kapdey safed hain, unhein pahna karo aur apney faut honey walon ko un mein kafan diya karo."
3567,"Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : safed kapdey pehna karo, wo ziyada pak aur ziyada umda hain."
3568,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : behtrin libas jis main tum apni qabron aur apni masjidon mein Allah sey miltey ho, safed libas hai."
3569,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs takabbur key sath apna kapda ghaseet kar chalta hai, qiyamat key din Allah Taala uski taraf ( rehmat ki) nazar nahin farmaeyga ."
3570,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney takabbur ki wajeh sey apna tehband ghasita, Allah Taala qiyamat key din uski taraf (rehmat ki) nazar nahin kerega. Atiya (Rahimahullah) ney bayan kya : balaat key maqam par mein ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) sey mila aur un sey abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ki is hadees ka zikr kya ke wo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey (ye hadees) bayan farmatey hain. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) ney apney kanon ki taraf ishara kar key farmaya : (ye sahih hai.) merey kanon ney isey (Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey) suna aur merey dil ney yad rakha ."
3571,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unkey paas sey eik Qureshi nojawan guzra jo motey kapdey ki chadar zamin par ghaseet raha tha. unhoney farmaya : bhatijey ! mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : jo shakhs takabbur ki wajeh sey apna kapda ghaseet kar chalta hai, qiyamat key din Allah Taala uski taraf ( rehmat ki) nazar nahin farmaeyga ."
3572,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney meri ya apni pindli key patthey key nichley hissey par haath rakha aur farmaya : ye tehband ki jagah hai. agar to (yahan tak rakhna) na chahey to nichey kar ley. agar to na chahey to (aur) nichey kar ley. agar to (itna sa ooncha bhi rakhna) na chahey to (maloom hona chahiye ke) tehband ka takhnon mein koi haq nahin. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney yehi riwayat Ali bin Muhammad key wastey sey bhi isi tarah Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey bayan ki hai."
3573,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Yaqub Johni Harqi (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha mainey Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : kya aap ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey tehband key barey mein koi farman suna hai? unhoney kaha : haan, mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna, aap farma rahey they : momin ka tehband (shalwaar, pent aur paeyjama waghera) uski pindliyon key nisf tak (buland) hota hai. us jagah aur takhnon key darmiyan rakhney mein is par gunah nahin. aur jo takhnon sey nichey ho, wo jahannam mein hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye baat teen baar farmaai : jo shakhs takabbur key sath tehband (zameen par) ghasitega, Allah Taala uski taraf (rehmat ki nazar sey) nahin dekhega."
3574,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Sufiyan bin Sehal! kapda (jayez had sey ziyada) na latka, Allah Taala kapda latkaaney walon ko pasand nahin farmata."
3575,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko koi kapda qamis sey ziyada pasand nahin tha."
3576,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ( jayez had sey ziyada) latkana tehband mein bhi hota hai, qamis mein bhi aur pagdi mein bhi. jo shakhs takabbur key tor par kisi bhi chiz ko latkaaey, qiyamat key din Allah Taala uski taraf (nazare-rehmat sey) nahin dekhega.) Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) key ustaad (abu-Bakar bin abi sheeba (Rahimahullah)) ney farmaya : ye kaisi naadir hadees hai!"
3577,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aisi qamis pehantey they jiski aastinein bhi chhoti hoti thin aur lambai bhi kam hoti thi ."
3578,"Hazrat Qurra bin Ayas Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur aap ki baiat ki. us waqt aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qamis ka batan khula huwa tha. Hazrat Urwa bin Abdullah (Rahimahullah) علیہم farmatey hain : mainey (Hazrat Qurra (Raziallahu anhu) key betey ( Muawiya bin Qurra (Rahimahullah) aur unkey betey ko sardiyon aur garmiyon mein jab bhi dekha , unkey batan khuley huye dekhey ."
3579,"Hazrat Suwed bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye aur hum sey shalwaar ka soda kya."
3580,"ummul-mominin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey daryaft kya gaya : aurat apna daman kitna latkaaey? aap ney farmaya : eik baalisht. mainey kaha : tab us (key qadmon ya pindliyon) sey kapda hat jaeyga. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik haath. us sey ziyada na latkaaey."
3581,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki azwaaje-mutahraat (Raziallahu anhu anhunna) ko eik haath daman ki ijazat di gaee thi . wo hamarey paas aatin to hum unhein sarkandey sey eik haath maap detey."
3582,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) sey ya Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey farmaya : tumhara daman eik haath hona chahiye .
3583,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney aurton key daman key barey mein farmaya : eik baalisht. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : tab to un ki pindliyan zahir ho jaeyngi . aap ney farmaya : tab eik haath (kafi hai.')
3584,"Hazrat Amr bin Hures (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko member par khutba irshad farmatey dekha jabkey aap ney siyah amama baandh rakha tha."
3585,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke (Fateh Makka key moqey par) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Makka Mukarrama mein dakhil huye to aap ney siyah amama baandha huwa tha.
3586,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Fateh Makka key din Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (Makka mein) dakhil huye to aap ney siyah amama baandha huwa tha.
3587,"Hazrat Amr bin Hures (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : goya main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekh raha hun jabkey aap key sar par siyah amama hai aur aap ney uskey dono sirey apney kandhon key darmiyan latkaaey huye hain."
3588,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney duniya mein resham pahna, wo aakhirat mein nahin pehnega."
3589,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney reshmi kapdey sey, aam resham sey aur motey resham sey mana farmaya."
3590,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney resham aur sona pehanney sey mana kya aur farmaya : wo duniya mein un (kafiron) key liye hai aur aakhirat mein hamarey liye."
3591,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney lakeer daar reshmi kapdey ka joda dekha to arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool! aap ye joda wufood key istaqbal aur Jumey key din pehanney key liye kharid lein. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey to wohi pahnta hai jiska aakhirat mein koi hissa nahin .
3592,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Zuber bin Awam (Raziallahu anhu) aur Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ko resham ki qameesein pehanney ki ijazat di kyonkey unhen khaarish ki takleef thi.
3593,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke wo bareek aur motey resham (ka kapda pehanney) sey mana kartey they, magar jo itna sa ho. phir (Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney) eik ungli sey ishara kya, phir dusri sey, phir teesri sey phir chauthi sey aur farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamen us sey mana farmaya kartey they."
3594,"Hazrat Asma bint abi Bakr (Raziallahu anha) key azad karda ghulam Hazrat abu-Umar Abdullah bin kaisaan Temi (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey dekha ke Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) ney amama kharid jis (key kinarey) par (resham key) nishan they. unhoney qainchi talab farmaai aur usey kaat dala. mainey Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar ye waqia bayan kya to unhoney farmaya : tajjub hai Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) par , (aur apni khaadima ko aawaz di) aey ladki ! Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka jubba lao. wo (Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka) jubba laee jiski aastinon, gireban aur dono taraf key chaak key kinaron par resham laga huwa tha."
3595,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apney baaein hath mein resham aur daain haath mein sona liya, phir dono haath buland kar key farmaya : ye dono cheezen meri ummat key mardon par haram aur un ki aurton key liye halal hain."
3596,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko eik hulla (chaadaron ka joda) hadiye key tor par pesh kya gaya jis ka taana ya bana resham ka bana huwa tha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wo hulla merey paas bhej diya. mainey khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool! main usey kya karun? kya main usey pehan sakta hun? aap ney farmaya : nahin, us sey faatimaaon ko odhniyaan bana dey."
3597,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas ( ghar sey) bahar tashrif laye . aap key eik haath mein reshmi kapda tha aur doosrey haath mein sona . aap ney farmaya : ye dono cheezen meri ummat key mardon par haram aur un ki aurton key liye halal hain."
3598,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki beti Hazrat Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ko dhaari daar reshmi qamis pehney dekha ."
3599,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey kisi ko Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ziyada sahibe-jamaal (khoobsoorat) nahin dekha jabke aap ney (baalon mein) kanghi ki hui thi aur surkh chadaren (tehband aur chadar) pehan rakhi thin ."
3600,"Hazrat Barida bin Huseb Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey dekha ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khutba dey rahey they ke itney mein Hazrat Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) aur Hazrat Husain (Raziallahu anhu) aa gaey. unhoney surkh qameesein pehan rakhi thin. kabhi girtey they, kabhi uthtey they. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (member sey) utar aaey aur unhein god mein utha liya. aur farmaya : Allah aur uskey Rasool ney sach farmaya : ( إنَّمَا أَمْوَالُکُمْ وَ أَوْلَادُکُمْ فِتْنَة )' tumharey maal aur tumhaari aulad eik aazmaaish hai. mainey unhein dekha to mujh sey sabr na huwa . phir aap ney khutba dena shuru kar diya."
3601,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney gehrey rang sey mana farmaya. (hadees key Raavi) Yazeed bayan kartey hain (ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) key shagrid) Hazrat Hasan bin Sehal (Rahimahullah) sey daryaft kya gaya : ( مُفَدَّمَ ) sey kya murad hai? unhoney farmaya : jo عُصفُر ( kusum) sey khub ranga gaya ho.
3602,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey kusum ka ranga huwa kapda pehanney sey mana farmaya. aur main nahin kehta : tumhen mana farmaya."
3603,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Saniya Azakhir sey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath aaye . aap meri taraf mutawajjeh huye jabke mainey Usfur sey rangi hui chadar odh rakhi thi. aap ney farmaya : ye kya hai? main samajh gaya ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kya chiz nagawar guzri hai. main ghar walon key paas gaya, unhoney tannur jala rakha tha. mainey wo (chadar) tannur mein dal di. agley din main khidmat mein hazir huwa to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Abdullah! chadar ka kya bana? mainey bata diya. aap ney farmaya : tu ney apney ghar walon mein sey kisi ko kyon na pahna di? aurton key liye to us (chadar key istimal) mein koi harj nahin."
3604,"Hazrat Qais bin Saad (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey yahan tashrif laye. hamney aap key nahaney key liye pani rakha to aap ney ghusl farmaya. phir mainey aapki khidmat mein zard chadar pesh ki. (aap ney odh li) mainey aap key pet Mubarak ki salwat par waras ka nishan dekha."
3605,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : khao, piyo, sadqa karo aur pahno , jab tak is mein fuzul kharchi ya takabbur ki aamezish na ho."
3606,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs shohrat wala libas pehnega, Allah Taala usey qiyamat key din zillat ka libas pahnaaeyga."
3607,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs duniya mein shohrat ka libas pehnega, Allah Taala usey qiyamat key din zillat ka libas pahnaaeyga, phir is mein aag bhadka dega."
3608,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney shohrat ka libas pahna, Allah Taala us sey (naraz ho kar) munh pher lega yahan tak key usey zaleel kar dega jab bhi zaleel kerey."
3609,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshad suna : jo bhi chamda rang liya jaey wo pak ho jata hai.
3610,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ummul-mominin Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ki azad karda londi ki eik mari hui bakri key paas sey guzrey jo unhen (azad karda londi ko) sadqey mein mili thi. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : unhoney uska chamdaa kyon na utaar liya ke usey rang kar us sey faeyda uthatey? haazirin ney arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! wo to murdar hai. aap ney farmaya : usey sirf khana haram hai.
3611,"Hazrat Salman (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : ummahat-mominin mein sey kisi ki eik bakri thi, wo mar gaee. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey paas sey guzrey to farmaya : agar uskey Malik uskey chamdey sey faeyda utha letey to unka kya nuqsan tha?"
3612,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney murda janwer key chamdey sey faeyda uthaney ka hukm diya jab usey rang liya jaey."
3613,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Akeem (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamarey paas Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka khat aaya ( jis mein ye tehreer tha) murdar key chamdey sey ya patthey sey faeyda na uthao."
3614,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key jootey ki do pattiyaan thin jinkey tasmey dohrey they."
3615,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key jooton ki do pattiyaan thin."
3616,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs jootey pehney to daaein jootey sey shuru karey aur jab utaarey to baaein sey shuru kerey."
3617,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi shakhs eik joota ya eik moza pehan kar na chaley, chahiye ke dono (jootey ya mozey) utaar ley ya dono pehan kar chaley."
3618,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney khadey-khadey jootey pehanney sey mana farmaya."
3619,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney khadey ho kar jootey pehanney sey mana farmaya."
3620,"Hazrat Barida bin Huseb Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Najaashi (Rahimahullah) ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko hadiya key tor par siyah saada mozon ka joda irsaal kya, chunanche aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney isey pahna."
3621,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bilashuba Yahudi aur Esai baalon ko nahin rangtey, chunanche tum un ki mukhalifat karo ."
3622,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : budhapey (key baalon) ka rang badalney key liye sab sey behtar chiz mahndi aur wasma hai."
3623,"Hazrat Usman bin Mohab (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : main ummul-mominin sayeda Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa . unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key chand baal nikal kar mujhey dikhaye jo mahndi aur wasma sey rangey huye they."
3624,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Fateh Makka key din Hazrat abu-Qahafa (Raziallahu anhu) ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir kya gaya. unka sar Saghama (safed ghaas) ki tarah (safed) tha. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : unhen un (key ghar) ki kisi khatoon key paas ley jao. wo (mahndi waghera key zariey sey) unkey baalon ka rang tabdeel kar dey. aur unhen siyah rang sey bachana."
3625,"Hazrat Suheb Romi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : behtareen chiz jis sey tum khizaab kartey ho, siyah rang hai. us sey tumhari aurton key dilon mein tumhari raghbat (aur mohabbat) ziyada hoti hai aur tumharey dushmanon key dilon main tumhara roab ziyada hota hai."
3626,"Hazrat Ubaid bin Juraij (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey sawal kya : mainey aap ko dekha hai ke aap waras key zariey sey apni dadhi ka rang zard kar letey hain (iski kya wajeh hai?) Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : mera apni dadhi ko zard rang karney ka sabab ye hai ke mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko apni dadhi Mubarak zard kartey dekha hai."
3627,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka guzar eik aadmi key paas sey huwa jisney mahndi ka khizaab kya huwa tha (baalon ka rang mahndi laga kar tabdeel kya huwa tha.) aap ney farmaya : ye kitna achcha hai! phir aap eik aur aadmi key paas sey guzrey jisney mahndi aur wasma ka khizaab kya huwa tha. aap ney farmaya : ye us sey ziyada achcha hai. phir eik aur aadmi key paas sey guzrey jisney zard khizaab kya huwa tha, aap ney farmaya : ye un sab sey achcha hai. Raavi hadees bayan kartey hain : (Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) key shagrid) Hazrat Taaus (Rahimahullah) zard khizaab istimal kartey they."
3628,"Hazrat abu-Juhaifa Wahab bin Abdullah Sawai (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap key ye baal safed they. unka ishara nichley hont aur thodi key darmiyan key baalon ki taraf tha."
3629,"Hazrat Humed (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, wo bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey daryaft kya gaya : kya Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney khizaab lagaya tha? unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key baal safed nahin huye, sirf dadhi key agley hissey mein satrah ya bees baal safed they."
3630,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key safed baalon ki taadad bees key qarib thi."
3631,"Hazrat Umme-Haani (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Makka mein dakhil huye to aap (key baalon) ki chaar latein, yani gundhi hui mendhiyan thin ."
3632,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : ehle-kitab baal (mang nikaley baghair) latkatey they, aur (arab key) mushrekin mang nikaltey they. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ehle-kitab ki muwaafiqat pasand thi, chunanche Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (shuru mein) sar key baal (ehle-kitab ki tarah) latka kar rakhtey they, phir baad mein aap mang nikalney lagey."
3633,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key taalu key peechey mang nikaalti thi . aur sar key agley hissey key baal latka deti thi ."
3634,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key baal sidhey they jo kanon aur kandhon key darmiyan tak hotey they."
3635,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key baal jumma sey kam aur wafra sey ziyada they."
3636,"Hazrat Wayl bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey dekha jabkey merey lambey baal they. aap ney farmaya : na Mubarak , na Mubarak . chunanche main gaya aur baal chhotey kar liye . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey (baal chhotey karwaaey huye) dekha to farmaya : mera maqsad tum sey (kuch kehna) nahin tha, wesay ye ziyada achey hain."
3637,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney qaza sey mana farmaya hai. Hazrat Nafey (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : qaza ka kya matlab hai? Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : wo ye hota hai ke bachey ka sar eik jagah sey (kuch hissa) moond diya jaey aur eik jagah sey (kuch hissa) chhod diya jaey ."
3638,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney qaza sey mana farmaya hai."
3639,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney chaandi ki anguthi banwai aur is mein Muhammad Rasoolullah key alfaz kanda karaaey. phir farmaya : koi shakhs meri is anguthi key naqsh ki tarah (apni anguthi par) naqsh na banwaey ."
3640,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik anguthi banwaai aur farmaya : hamney anguthi banwaai hai aur is par eik naqsh banwaya hai, chunanche aur koi shakhs is tarah key naqsh na banwaey ."
3641,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney chaandi ki anguthi banwaai jis mein Habshi nagina tha. uska naqsh Muhammad Rasoolullah tha.
3642,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney soney ki anguthi pehanney sey mana farmaya."
3643,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney soney ki anguthi sey mana farmaya."
3644,"ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Najaashi (Rahimahullah) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein soney ki eik anguthi hadiye key tor par bheji, is mein Habshi nageena juda huwa tha. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney is mein dilchaspi na letey huye usey lakdi sey ya apni kuch ungliyon sey pakda, phir apni nawaasi Hazrat Amaama bint Abul-Aas (Raziallahu anha) ko bula kar farmaya : beti ! ye zewar pehan lo ."
3645,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni anguthi ka nagina hatheli ki taraf rakhtey they."
3646,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney chaandi ki anguthi pahni jis mein Habshi nagina tha. aap naginey ko hatheli ki andruni taraf rakhtey they."
3647,Hazrat Abdullah bin Jaafar bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney daain haath mein anguthi pehantey they.
3648,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney bayan kya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey is mein aur us mein, yani chhangliya (chhoti ungli) aur angoothey mein, anguthi pehanney sey mana farmaya."
3649,"Hazrat abu-Talha Zaid bin Sehal Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : farishtey us ghar mein dakhil nahin hotey jis mein kutta ya tasweer ho."
3650,"Hazrat Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : farishtey us ghar mein dakhil nahin hotey jis mein kutta ya tasweer ho."
3651,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Jibril (Alaihissalam) ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey eik khas waqt par tashrif laney ka wada kiya. unkey aaney mein takheer (deri) hui to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (ghar sey) bahar tashrif laye. dekha to Jibril (Alaihissalam) darwazey par khadey they. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aap ko andar aaney mein kya rukawat thi? unhoney farmaya : ghar main eik kutta hai aur hum us ghar mein dakhil nahin hotey jis mein kutta ya tasweer ho.
3652,Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik khatoon ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya ke unka shohar jihad mein gaya huwa hai. usney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ijazat talab ki ke wo ghar mein khajoor key darkht ki tasweer banwaa ley. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney isey mana farma diya.
3653,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey ghar key andar apney eik taaqchey par tasweeron wala parda latka diya. jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye to aap ney isey phaad dala. mainey uskey do gaddey bana liye, phir mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko un mein sey eik gaddey par tek lagaey huye dekha."
3654,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney soney ki anguthi sey aur (surkh) zeen posh sey mana farmaya."
3655,"Sahabi Rasool Hazrat Abu Rihaana Shamoon bin Zaid Azdi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) cheetey (ki khaal) par sawari karney sey mana farmaya kartey they."
3656,"Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) cheetey (ki khaal) par sawar honey sey mana farmaya kartey they."
